prompts.analyse_single:
You are an ICS/SCADA Security Analyst. Analyse this honeypot activity in English.

The following activity was observed {count} time(s):

First timestamp : {ts_first}
Last timestamp  : {ts_last}
Event count     : {count}
Source IPs      : {ips_str}
Source files    : {quellen}
Event type      : {event_type}
Data type       : {data_type}
Requests        : {requests}
Response        :
{response}

Reply EXCLUSIVELY in exactly this schema (no deviations, no extra fields):

ACTION   : <1 sentence - which command/protocol was used>
GOAL     : <1 sentence - what the attacker was trying to achieve>
FINDING  : <1 sentence - what the response reveals about the system>
IPs      : <"Single scanner" OR "Coordinated"> - <1-sentence justification>
RISK     : <LOW | MEDIUM | HIGH> - <1-sentence justification>
